text: Oxana Saichuk (born 9 December 1995) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2018 Asian Games. == References == Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
